data.description: Enjoy maintenance free exterior living in this beautiful condo in the Hidden Creek Community of Trader's Point! Step into an inviting entry way that leads to an open floor plan.   The cozy family room has vaulted ceilings, and a corner wood burning fireplace, creating an impressive space for relaxation and family gatherings. Just outside of the family room is a 2nd level covered deck that overlooks a tranquil wooded area. Updated appliances remain in the kitchen. Built in microwave & refrigerator new in 2019. Breakfast bar adjoins the kitchen space.2 baths & 2 spacious bedrooms with large walk-in closets. Large laundry room, washer and dryer and a chrome shelving rack, all included. Additional storage closet just steps away. Designated parking space close to building. Amenities include Clubhouse with fitness center, pool, and tennis courts. Just minutes from Eagle Creek Reservoir, shopping and restaurants on Whitestown Parkway and 20-minute commute to downtown. HVAC replaced in 2019.
